{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2195504, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 425215, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "看人，不过通常来说老师把学生推荐外校很容易", "timestamp": 1627953601, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2195508, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 425215, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "建议问清楚是哪个系/哪个学校", "timestamp": 1627953649, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2195690, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 425215, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "如果是正常老师，应该是会帮忙推荐的。\n但是推荐并不等于保证能推上，如果有需要夏令营考核啥的，这些应该还是要靠自己的（不过感觉应该问题不大）", "timestamp": 1627955998, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2196532, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 425215, "reply_to": 2195690, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 诶？老师推荐不是难道不是说“xx啊，我这儿有个学生挺不错的，但我们这儿名额不够了，你把他收了吧，他说也愿意去”", "timestamp": 1627962675, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2196535, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 425215, "reply_to": 2195690, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 然后就走流程啥的", "timestamp": 1627962696, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2196553, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 425215, "reply_to": 2195690, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 九推不需要夏令营考核，只需要面试", "timestamp": 1627962853, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2196557, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 425215, "reply_to": 2196553, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 也需要面试的吧，不过外校的教授通常名额很多，有老师推荐的话通过的可能性极大", "timestamp": 1627962906, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 3, "pid": 425215, "reply": 7, "tag": null, "text": "认识的老师在得知我成绩几乎铁定不能留在本系读研后，说让我现在帮他做个小项目，九推时他可以帮我推荐到外系或外校\n老师说这种话一般靠谱吗", "timestamp": 1627953331, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1627962908, "url": "", "vote": {}}}